<h2>James Pinkerton to speak at Brown Bag Luncheon, September 29.</h2>



<h3>The Progress & Freedom Foundation<br>
presents: <br><br></h3>

<h3>James P. Pinkerton</h3>
<h4>to discuss his book,</h4>
<h3><i>What Comes Next:<br>
The End of Big Government-<br>
and the New Paradigm Ahead</i></h3>
on<br>
Friday, September 29, 1995<br><br>
at<br>
12:00 PM<br><br>
for<br>
A Luncheon
hosted by<br>
Joseph E Seagrams & Sons, Inc.<p>

Please join us at the Joseph E. Seagrams & Sons condominium at<br>
3030 K Street, NW, Penthouse #214, Washington Harbor<br><p>
*****************************************************<p>
To confirm attendance, please notify <br>
Katherine Epler at (202)484-2312 or by fax (202)484-9326.<p>

Parking:  As you pull into the driveway of the complex, you will see PMI <br>parking to your left.  The parking lot is in Building 3000<br>
adjacent to 3030 K Street.


