http://www.lead-inst.org:80/cir/cases/fecdc.html 204.71.237.80 19970217135839 text/html 54352
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 13:59:20 GMT
