<title>Gary Bauer's Monthly Letters</title>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000">

<center>
<img src = "/townhall/FRC/letters/letterbn.gif">
</center>
<br>

Each month, <a href="/townhall/FRC/whois/bauer.html">Gary L. 
Bauer</a>, President of the Family Research Council, writes a letter 
to the friends of FRC that highlights a current topic, analyzes a key 
family issue, or describes an ongoing or new activity of the Council. 
These personal letters both describe the FRC President's perspective 
on the most pressing family issues and chronicle the development of 
FRC projects and programs to address those issues. These letters give 
friends of FRC an inside, in-depth look at the Council's work.

<p>
<center><img src="/townhall/FRC/images/yllwline.gif"></center>
<p>

<img src="/townhall/FRC/gary.gif" width=200 height=275 align=left 
vspace=3 hspace=9>

<p>

Make sure to read <a href="/townhall/FRC/letters/jan97.html">the most 
recent</a> letter.  Previous letters are also available, so feel free 
to browse them at your leisure. If you would like to see a letter that 
is not available here, please let us know and we'll try and get it for 
you.

<ul>

<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/apr96.html">April 1996</A>
<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/may96.html">May 1996</A>
<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/jun96.html">June 1996</A>
<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/jul96.html">July 1996</A>
<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/aug96.html">August 1996</A>
<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/sept96.html">September 1996</A>
<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/oct96.html">October 1996</A>
<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/nov96.html">November 1996</A>
<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/dec96.html">December 1996</A>
<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/jan97.html">January 1997</A>

</ul>

<p><br><br><br>
