<DOCHDR>
http://www.lead-inst.org:80/empower/sp-11175.html 204.71.237.80 19970210131912 text/html 7974
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 13:19:59 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 02-Jul-96 20:54:54 GMT
