http://www.lead-inst.org:80/cir/issues/fa-pc.html 204.71.237.80 19970210122207 text/html 6075
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 12:22:54 GMT
